data.description: Introducing a charming property located in Bernalillo, New Mexico, this delightful home offers a range of desirable features and amenities. Situated on a generous .63 acre lot, this residence boasts side yard access and a rare irrigation right to the ditch, ensuring lush greenery for your outdoor space. Space for an RV which offers an electric 50 amp service  & water access. The property includes a convenient storage building with a garage door, providing ample room for all your storage needs, and comes equipped with electricity for added convenience. New TPO roof with warranty.  Enjoy the owned solar panel too. Featuring a spacious layout, the home comprises three bedrooms and two bathrooms, ensuring plenty of space for comfortable living.
